  <name>HTTP_Common</name>
  <channel>pear.php.net</channel>
  <summary>Common classes for HTTP packages</summary>
  <description>
This package defines a set of common classes for use by the various HTTP
packages, currently classes available are:
 * HTTP_Common_Headers: a lightweight class that represent a set of headers,
   it provide an array and object access interface;
 * HTTP_Common_Message: a base class for HTTP messages as defined by the
   RFC2616, child messages can be request, response or entity.
  </description>
